+
+```
+src/
+  chatbot.py               # Basic multi-turn chatbot
+  chatbot_streaming.py     # Streaming + prompt caching version
+  requirements.txt
+
+demo/
+  raw/
+    logs/execution_log.md  # Execution log and simulation notes
+  working/
