+# AI Tool Test Scorecard
+
+Fill this out after recording each demo. One scorecard per tool.  
+**Label:** Scores must be based on live testing — do not estimate. Mark `[UNSCORED]` until tested.
+
+---
+
+## Tool Info
+
+| Field          | Value              |
+|----------------|--------------------|
+| Tool name      | [TOOL NAME]        |
+| URL            | [URL]              |
+| Tested on      | [YYYY-MM-DD]       |
+| Tested by      | [NAME]             |
+| Plan used      | Free / Pro / Trial |
+| Live tested?   | Yes / No / [SIMULATED] |
+
+---
+
+## Scoring Rubric
+
+Rate each dimension 1–5:
+
+| Score | Meaning                                        |
+|-------|------------------------------------------------|
+| 1     | Poor — broken, confusing, or useless           |
+| 2     | Below average — works but with major issues    |
+| 3     | Average — functional, nothing special          |
+| 4     | Good — solid, would recommend with caveats     |
+| 5     | Excellent — best in class for this dimension   |
+
+---
+
+## Scorecard
+
+### 1. Ease of Use
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> Can a non-technical user start producing value in under 5 minutes?
+
+Notes:
+- Onboarding experience:
+- Learning curve:
+- UI clarity:
+
+---
+
+### 2. Output Quality
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> How good is the actual output — text, image, video, code, etc.?
+
+Notes:
+- First-try quality:
+- Consistency across multiple runs:
+- Comparison to manual baseline:
+
+---
+
+### 3. Speed
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> How fast does it go from input to usable output?
+
+Notes:
+- Time from prompt to result:
+- Acceptable for real workflow use?:
+
+---
+
+### 4. Practical Business Value
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> Does this tool solve a real, recurring business problem — not just a demo trick?
+
+Notes:
+- Use cases it covers:
+- Use cases it misses:
+- Integrates with existing workflows?:
+
+---
+
+### 5. Creator / Solopreneur Usefulness
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> Is this useful for a one-person business — content creator, freelancer, consultant?
+
+Notes:
+- Time saved per week (estimate):
+- Replaces which manual tasks:
+
+---
+
+### 6. Automation Potential
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> Can this tool be triggered via API, Zapier, Make, or webhooks to run without manual input?
+
+Notes:
+- Has API?: Yes / No
+- Zapier / Make connector?: Yes / No
+- Webhook support?: Yes / No
+- Best automation use case:
+
+---
+
+### 7. Monetization Potential
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> Can someone use this tool to directly generate revenue — for a client, a product, or a service?
+
+Notes:
+- How a creator could charge for output:
+- Client use case:
+- Product/template idea:
+
+---
+
+### 8. Free Plan Limits
+**Score:** [1–5] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+> How generous is the free tier for real use (not just a trial)?
+
+Notes:
+- What free plan includes:
+- Main free plan restrictions:
+- Credit/usage cap:
+- Paid plan starting price: $[X]/mo
+
+---
+
+### 9. Best Use Case
+**[UNSCORED — fill after testing]**
+
+> In one sentence, what is this tool best for?
+
+[E.g. "Best for creating AI-generated presentation decks in under 5 minutes without design skills."]
+
+---
+
+### 10. Verdict
+**Overall Score:** [X / 50] `[UNSCORED]`
+
+**Tier:**
+- 45–50: **S-tier** — must-use, recommend immediately
+- 35–44: **A-tier** — strong tool, worth it for the right user
+- 25–34: **B-tier** — solid for specific use cases
+- 15–24: **C-tier** — limited, use only if no alternative
+- Below 15: **D-tier** — avoid or wait for improvement
+
+**One-line verdict:**
+> [E.g. "Canva AI is an A-tier tool for non-designers who need fast, professional visual content."]
+
+**Recommend to:**
+- [ ] Complete beginners
+- [ ] Solopreneurs / freelancers
+- [ ] Small business owners
+- [ ] Content creators
+- [ ] Agencies
+- [ ] Developers
+
+**Would pay for it?** Yes / No / Maybe  
+**Would demo again?** Yes / No  
+
+---
+
+## Comparison Notes (optional)
+
+> How does this tool compare to the closest alternative?
+
+| Dimension      | [This Tool] | [Competitor] | Winner |
+|----------------|-------------|--------------|--------|
+| Ease of use    |             |              |        |
+| Output quality |             |              |        |
+| Free plan      |             |              |        |
+| Price          |             |              |        |
+| Best for       |             |              |        |
