+# Caption & Title Template
+
+Platform-specific copy for every AI tool demo. Fill in bracketed fields per tool.  
+**Label:** Copy is planned / template — not published. Publish only after manual review.
+
+---
+
+## Title Formula Bank
+
+Use one of these formulas per video. A/B test two per upload.
+
+| Formula                         | Example                                              |
+|---------------------------------|------------------------------------------------------|
+| "I tested X so you don't have to" | "I tested Canva AI for a week so you don't have to" |
+| "X in Y minutes"                | "Make a pitch deck in 3 minutes with Gamma AI"       |
+| "X replaced my [task]"          | "Perplexity just replaced my Google habit"           |
+| "X vs Y — which is better?"     | "ChatGPT vs Claude — which should you use in 2026?"  |
+| "How I use X to [result]"       | "How I use ElevenLabs to clone my voice for free"    |
+| "Stop using X. Use Y instead."  | "Stop using Google. Use Perplexity instead."         |
+| "The [tool] tutorial nobody made" | "The Runway tutorial nobody made"                  |
+| "Honest review: X"              | "Honest review: Notion AI — worth it?"               |
+
+**Title rules:**
+- Keep under 60 characters for YouTube (shows fully in search)
+- Include the tool name (SEO)
+- Include the year if the topic is time-sensitive
+- No clickbait — your score must match the title's energy
+
+---
+
+## YouTube
+
+**Title A:** `[TOOL NAME]: [Benefit or result] in [Time] ([Year])`  
+**Title B:** `I tested [TOOL NAME] — here's the honest verdict`
+
+**Description template:**
+```
+[1-sentence hook — what you tested and why it matters]
+
+In this video:
+→ [What you demonstrated, bullet 1]
+→ [What you demonstrated, bullet 2]
+→ [Your score and verdict]
+
+⏱ Timestamps:
+0:00 – Hook
+0:10 – What is [TOOL]?
+0:30 – Live demo: [specific test]
+[X]:00 – Results
+[X]:30 – Score & verdict
+[X]:45 – Subscribe / CTA
+
+🔗 Try [TOOL NAME]: [URL]
+📁 Free resource: [link or "coming soon"]
+
+🔔 Subscribe for a new AI tool review every week.
+
+---
+Tags: [tool name], [tool name] tutorial, [tool name] review, [tool name] 2026, ai tools, best ai tools, [category] ai, [use case] ai tool
+```
+
+**Tags (add tool-specific + these evergreen tags):**
+```
+ai tools 2026, best ai tools, ai tool review, solopreneur tools, creator tools, automation tools, ai tutorial, [tool name], [tool name] review, [tool name] tutorial
+```
+
+---
+
+## TikTok
+
+**Caption template:**
+```
+[Hook line from script — 1 punchy sentence] 🤖
+
+[What you tested — 1 sentence]
+[The result — 1 sentence]
+My score: [X]/5
+
+Full breakdown → link in bio
+
+#aitools #[toolname] #ai #tutorial #solopreneur #contentcreator #automation #[niche]
+```
+
+**Hashtag strategy:**
+- 3–5 niche tags (`#canvaai`, `#aidesign`, `#aitools`)
+- 2–3 broad tags (`#ai`, `#tutorial`, `#contentcreator`)
+- 1 trending tag (check TikTok trending page day of posting)
+- Max 7–9 total — don't spam
+
+---
+
+## Instagram Reels
+
+**Caption template:**
+```
+Tested [TOOL] so you don't have to 👀
+
+[Pain point sentence]
+[What the tool does in one line]
+[Your verdict sentence]
+
+Score: [X]/5
+
+Full tutorial on YouTube → link in bio
+
+#aitools #[toolname] #artificialintelligence #contentcreator #solopreneur #digitaltools #aiautomation #[niche]
+```
+
+**Notes:**
+- First line is the hook — it shows before "more" cutoff
+- Keep under 150 characters for the first line
+- Use line breaks — walls of text get ignored
+
+---
+
+## YouTube Shorts
+
+**Title:** `[Bold claim] #Shorts`  
+Example: `"I replaced Google with this AI tool #Shorts"`
+
+**Description:**
+```
+[Tool name] demo — [one line]. Full tutorial linked.
+```
+
+---
+
+## Twitter / X
