+- [ ] Do Not Disturb / notifications off
+- [ ] Microphone tested — peaks at -12dB to -6dB
+- [ ] Script reviewed (`voiceover-script-template.md`)
+- [ ] Shot list printed or on second screen
+
+---
+
+## Standard Shot List (adapt per demo)
+
+### Shot 1 — Cold Open / Hook
+- **Scene:** Face cam (Scene 2) OR screen capture (Scene 1)
+- **Duration:** 3–7 seconds
+- **Content:** Hook line — bold claim, question, or shocking result
+- **Notes:** No intro. Start with impact.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 2 — Tool Homepage
+- **Scene:** Browser full screen (Scene 1)
+- **Duration:** 3–5 seconds
+- **Content:** Navigate to the tool's URL. Let it fully load. Don't narrate yet.
+- **Notes:** Shows audience the real UI. Establishes credibility.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 3 — Sign In / Onboarding (first-time only)
+- **Scene:** Browser (Scene 1)
+- **Duration:** 10–20 seconds or cut in edit
+- **Content:** Show the sign-up or free plan access point
+- **Notes:** Blur any personal email. Speed up in post if slow.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+- [ ] N/A (skipping for this demo)
+
+---
+
+### Shot 4 — Dashboard / Main UI
+- **Scene:** Browser full screen (Scene 1)
+- **Duration:** 5–8 seconds
+- **Content:** A clean view of the main workspace or dashboard
+- **Notes:** Orient the viewer before going deep.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 5 — Input / Prompt Entry (ZOOM)
+- **Scene:** Zoom scene (Scene 4) or manual zoom in post
+- **Duration:** 5–15 seconds
+- **Content:** Type your prompt or configure your input. Show exactly what you typed.
+- **Notes:** Slow down. Viewers need to read your input.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 6 — Processing / Generation
+- **Scene:** Browser (Scene 1)
+- **Duration:** Full duration — do not cut during generation on first run
+- **Content:** The tool thinking / generating
+- **Notes:** Let the real generation time show. Honest pacing. Speed up in post if > 30 seconds.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 7 — Output / Result (ZOOM on key detail)
+- **Scene:** Scene 4 (zoom) or Scene 1
+- **Duration:** 10–20 seconds
+- **Content:** Show the full output. Zoom into the best or most impressive part.
+- **Notes:** Read part of the output aloud if it's text. Let image/video outputs play in full.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 8 — Reaction / Commentary
+- **Scene:** Face cam (Scene 2)
+- **Duration:** 5–15 seconds
+- **Content:** Honest reaction. What's good. What's not. One specific insight.
+- **Notes:** Don't oversell. Authentic reactions build trust.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 9 — Second Test / Edge Case (optional but valuable)
+- **Scene:** Browser (Scene 1) + Zoom
+- **Duration:** 20–40 seconds
+- **Content:** Try a harder prompt, a different use case, or push a limitation
+- **Notes:** Showing failures honestly is content gold.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+- [ ] Skipping
+
+---
+
+### Shot 10 — Verdict / Scorecard
+- **Scene:** Face cam (Scene 2) or screen share of scorecard
+- **Duration:** 10–20 seconds
+- **Content:** Your score + one-line verdict. "I'd give this a 4/5 for..."
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+### Shot 11 — CTA / Outro
+- **Scene:** Face cam (Scene 2) → Outro card (Scene 5)
+- **Duration:** 5–10 seconds
+- **Content:** Subscribe / follow / link in bio. Tease next video.
+- **Notes:** Smile. Make eye contact with camera.
+- Timestamp: `__:__`
+- [ ] Recorded
+
+---
+
+## Short-Form Shot List (60-second cut)
+
+For TikTok / Reels / Shorts, use only:
+
+| # | Shot                          | Max duration |
+|---|-------------------------------|--------------|
+| 1 | Hook (on camera or text)      | 3 s          |
