+# Thumbnail Brief Template
+
+Art direction for every AI tool demo thumbnail. Hand this to a designer or use with Canva / Adobe Express / Midjourney.  
+**Label:** Template — requires manual design execution.
+
+---
+
+## YouTube Thumbnail Spec
+
+| Field          | Value                    |
+|----------------|--------------------------|
+| Dimensions     | 1280 × 720 px            |
+| File format    | JPG or PNG               |
+| Max file size  | 2 MB                     |
+| Safe zone      | Leave 100 px margin on all sides for mobile cropping |
+
+---
+
+## Thumbnail Formula Options
+
+### Formula A — Face + Result
+> Your face (surprised / impressed / skeptical) on left or right.  
+> A screenshot of the tool's output in the remaining space.  
+> Bold text overlay: your verdict or the hook.
+
+**When to use:** You're on camera in the video. High trust, humanizes the channel.
+
+---
+
+### Formula B — Screen + Text Punch
+> A clean screenshot of the AI tool's most impressive output.  
+> Large, bold text overlay (2–4 words max).  
+> Colored border or glow to make it pop.
+
+**When to use:** Faceless content or when the output is visually striking enough to carry the thumbnail.
+
+---
+
+### Formula C — Before / After
+> Left side: the old way (manual, slow, painful).  
+> Right side: the AI tool's result.  
+> "vs" or arrow divider in the center.
+
+**When to use:** Comparison or transformation demos.
+
+---
+
+### Formula D — Score Badge
+> Tool logo or screenshot on the left.  
+> Large score badge (e.g., "4.2 / 5") on the right.  
+> Star rating or colored tier badge (S / A / B / C).
+
+**When to use:** Review / rating videos. Sets expectation of objectivity.
+
+---
+
+## Thumbnail Brief — Fill In Per Demo
+
+| Field                  | Value                              |
+|------------------------|------------------------------------|
+| Tool name              | [TOOL NAME]                        |
+| Formula chosen         | A / B / C / D                      |
+| Background color       | [hex or description, e.g. #0A0A0A dark] |
+| Primary text           | [Max 4 words — the hook]           |
+| Secondary text         | [Optional — tool name or score]    |
+| Face expression        | Surprised / Impressed / Skeptical / N/A |
+| Screenshot to use      | [Describe which output to capture] |
+| Accent color           | [hex or brand color]               |
+| Font style             | Bold sans-serif (e.g. Impact, Bebas, Anton) |
+| Border / glow          | Yes / No — color: [hex]            |
+
+---
+
+## AI Image Generation Prompts (for Midjourney / DALL-E / Canva AI)
+
+**For Formula B (screen + text):**
+> "YouTube thumbnail, dark background, glowing terminal or browser window showing AI-generated text, large white bold text reading '[YOUR HOOK]', neon [color] accent border, 1280x720, high contrast, cinematic"
+
+**For Formula A (face + result):**
+> "YouTube thumbnail, split composition, [left/right]: shocked developer face looking at camera, [right/left]: bright glowing AI output on screen, bold white text overlay '[YOUR HOOK]', dark dramatic lighting"
+
+**For Formula C (before/after):**
+> "YouTube thumbnail, split screen, left side: messy chaotic manual work (grey, dull), right side: clean polished AI output (bright, colorful), center: bold arrow or 'vs', text: '[Tool] changes everything', 1280x720"
+
+**For Formula D (score badge):**
+> "YouTube thumbnail, dark background, [tool] logo left side, large gold star rating badge right side showing '4.5/5', bold white text '[TOOL NAME] — Honest Review', professional tech aesthetic"
+
+---
+
+## Short-Form Thumbnail / Cover Frame (TikTok / Reels / Shorts)
+
+| Field          | Value                    |
+|----------------|--------------------------|
+| Dimensions     | 1080 × 1920 px (9:16)    |
+| Cover frame    | Use the most visually striking moment — usually the output reveal |
+| Text overlay   | Tool name + hook (2 lines max) |
+| Position       | Top third of frame (avoids UI overlap on TikTok) |
+
+**AI generation prompt:**
+> "Vertical 9:16 social media cover, dark background, AI tool interface screenshot centered, bold white text top: '[TOOL NAME]', subtitle: '[HOOK]', neon glow accent, high energy, mobile-first"
+
+---
+
+## Design Checklist
+
+- [ ] Text readable at thumbnail size (check at 120×68 px preview)
+- [ ] No more than 3–4 words of large text
+- [ ] High contrast between text and background
+- [ ] Face (if used) visible and expressive — not cropped
+- [ ] No copyright violations — use your own screenshots
+- [ ] Exported at correct dimensions and under 2 MB
+- [ ] Tested in YouTube Studio preview on mobile
